aws:cdk:cloudformation:props.description: KMS CMK used for message queue test
KMS CMK used for message queue test
Processes objects put into the S3 Bucket for inbound payloads
Polls the failed queue to put S3 Objects into the failed Bucket for follow-up
Triggers the failure lambda hourly to get messages from the failure queue
aws:cdk:cloudformation:props.name: MessageTestFailureTrigger
